graph TB
    User[用户请求] --> Router{路由分发}
    
    Router -->|登录/注册/查询 | Sync[同步处理]
    Sync --> DB[(数据库)]
    DB --> SyncResponse[同步响应]
    
    Router -->|AI 聊天/语音 | Async[异步处理]
    Async --> Thread[后台线程]
    Thread --> EventLoop[asyncio 事件循环]
    EventLoop --> LLM[大模型 API]
    EventLoop --> TTS[TTS WebSocket]
    EventLoop --> ASR[ASR WebSocket]
    LLM --> MQ[消息队列]
    TTS --> MQ
    MQ --> SSE[SSE 流式推送]
    SSE --> Frontend[前端实时显示]
